  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1705278702\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Planeticus is a multiplayer 2D space strategy game. The most enjoyable experience will be achieved in the company of friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/2284c7190514ecd4894a3d5455b75c6e.webp?t=1705278702\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Exchange spaceships for the right to own the desired planets and receive random resources for your collection. You can transfer resources between your planets, increasing armor or for other purposes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/06ecf5ebb8f9cd83c84c74583aef8158.poster.avif?t=1705278702\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/06ecf5ebb8f9cd83c84c74583aef8158.webm?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/06ecf5ebb8f9cd83c84c74583aef8158.mp4?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/f2e3013acb5cfc617b338e4b2b1df3e4.webp?t=1705278702\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>By collecting all 5 types of resources on one planet, you will turn it into a super planet that will begin to generate ships for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/a2acbaa29ad7bade6122814644f038df.poster.avif?t=1705278702\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/a2acbaa29ad7bade6122814644f038df.webm?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/a2acbaa29ad7bade6122814644f038df.mp4?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/3756f2a2f5292449329fba17de609fc3.webp?t=1705278702\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Will you send spaceships to attack or protect the necessary planets?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/9e76a1f06dfb189f4afba296bbaff7cc.poster.avif?t=1705278702\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/9e76a1f06dfb189f4afba296bbaff7cc.webm?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/9e76a1f06dfb189f4afba296bbaff7cc.mp4?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/71b5354205e93c4bd9ee480b676c0c8b.webp?t=1705278702\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Build walls between planets to protect yourself from enemies. You can also build them unexpectedly to instantly destroy enemy ships. It all depends on your ingenuity!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/d1c82b2a73c19004ff541a5a7866727e.poster.avif?t=1705278702\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/d1c82b2a73c19004ff541a5a7866727e.webm?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/d1c82b2a73c19004ff541a5a7866727e.mp4?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/eb90f5ab9eeec13264db2256e06cf637.webp?t=1705278702\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>The size of the map is determined by the number of players. Each game will give you a different list of planets. All planets will have a random name, map position, appearance, and resource element. Also, players are given a random home planet at start and there will always be a different distance between players. More accidents to the god of accidents!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/7aad7259f41a4f958078d95eaa599bfb.webp?t=1705278702\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Who are you: a pathetic space worm or a respected ruler of the galaxies?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1705278702\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Planeticus is a multiplayer 2D space strategy game. The most enjoyable experience will be achieved in the company of friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/2284c7190514ecd4894a3d5455b75c6e.webp?t=1705278702\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Exchange spaceships for the right to own the desired planets and receive random resources for your collection. You can transfer resources between your planets, increasing armor or for other purposes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/06ecf5ebb8f9cd83c84c74583aef8158.poster.avif?t=1705278702\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/06ecf5ebb8f9cd83c84c74583aef8158.webm?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/06ecf5ebb8f9cd83c84c74583aef8158.mp4?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/f2e3013acb5cfc617b338e4b2b1df3