 to protect yourself from enemies. You can also build them unexpectedly to instantly destroy enemy ships. It all depends on your ingenuity!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/d1c82b2a73c19004ff541a5a7866727e.poster.avif?t=1705278702\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/d1c82b2a73c19004ff541a5a7866727e.webm?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/d1c82b2a73c19004ff541a5a7866727e.mp4?t=1705278702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/eb90f5ab9eeec13264db2256e06cf637.webp?t=1705278702\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>The size of the map is determined by the number of players. Each game will give you a different list of planets. All planets will have a random name, map position, appearance, and resource element. Also, players are given a random home planet at start and there will always be a different distance between players. More accidents to the god of accidents!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607230/extras/7aad7259f41a4f958078d95eaa599bfb.webp?t=1705278702\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Who are you: a pathetic space worm or a respected ruler of the galaxies?",
